(14924,	'_transient_fd32b892cf53311fea6335b62eaad92b_version_data',	'a:4:{s:4:\"date\";s:10:\"2014-04-10\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.0.3\";s:6:\"update\";s:96:\"Fix - Ensures the \'headers already sent\' notice does not display, by starting the output buffer.\";s:9:\"changelog\";a:5:{s:7:\"headers\";a:11:{s:12:\"content-type\";s:10:\"text/plain\";s:14:\"content-length\";s:3:\"838\";s:10:\"connection\";s:5:\"close\";s:4:\"date\";s:29:\"Tue, 12 Aug 2014 07:50:33 GMT\";s:13:\"last-modified\";s:29:\"Tue, 15 Apr 2014 10:43:31 GMT\";s:4:\"etag\";s:34:\"\"0b1ef7d7ac7c4d2c24157cd060ebef89\"\";s:13:\"accept-ranges\";s:5:\"bytes\";s:6:\"server\";s:8:\"AmazonS3\";s:7:\"x-cache\";s:20:\"Miss from cloudfront\";s:3:\"via\";s:64:\"1.1 ae61a16dbb6cef89be9f99c05891f398.cloudfront.net (CloudFront)\";s:11:\"x-amz-cf-id\";s:56:\"dwEvjWdlHNcPqalY26bqtfGb5u3eUpm23WoIXT9z4Te-3WXB71rSmQ==\";}s:4:\"body\";s:838:\"*** WooCommerce Instagram Changelog ***\n\n2014.04.10 - version 1.0.3\n* Fix - Ensures the \'headers already sent\' notice does not display, by starting the output buffer.\n* Fix - Fixes the connect/disconnect redirect URL to point to the correct admin screen if using WooCommerce 2.1 or higher.\n  /classes/class-woocommerce-instagram-integration.php\n\n2014.04.01 - version 1.0.2\n* Fix - Corrects the \"page\" parameter in the admin notice URL, for WooCommerce 2.1+ users.\n  /classes/class-woocommerce-instagram-admin.php\n\n2013.11.06 - version 1.0.1\n* /assets/css/admin.css - Optimises CSS to use correct LESS syntax and to correctly style the write panel icon in WooCommerce 2.0.x.\n* /classes/class-woocommerce-instagram-admin.php - Optimises WooCommerce 2.0.x and 2.1.x compatibility switching.\n\n2013.10.29 - version 1.0.0\n * First release. Woo!\";s:8:\"response\";a:2:{s:4:\"code\";i:200;s:7:\"message\";s:2:\"OK\";}s:7:\"cookies\";a:0:{}s:8:\"filename\";N;}}',	'no'),
