(749,	1,	'2014-07-14 03:14:19',	'2014-07-14 03:14:19',	'<ul>\r\n	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>What is Keenlo?\r\n</b></span><span class=\"s2\">Keenlo is the best way to discover fitness classes and experiences in your community and online.We also help fitness businesses get online and be more successful. By offering the first easy to use, affordable tools for tasks like online marketing, scheduling classes, collecting payments and staying in touch with clients, Keenlo allows fitness professionals to spend more of their time teaching, and less time behind a desk.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s2\">Take a look at some of Keenlo<a href=\"http://keenlo.com/how-it-works/\"><span class=\"s3\"><b>’s features here</b></span></a>, and take the pain out of running your business.</span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s2\">We take the work out of working out by allowing anyone to organize, discover, book and share fitness classes online.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>How do I use Keenlo?\r\n</b></span><span class=\"s2\">Using Keenlo is simple! Create your profile and then start browsing for fitness classes near you. Once you find a class you’d like to take, reserve and pay for it in one simple click. You can also add fitness studios and classes to your favorites list to make booking and paying for classes easier than ever before.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s2\">If you’re a fit pro, learn more about how Keenlo can help you <a href=\"http://keenlo.com/how-it-works/\"><span class=\"s3\"><b>manage and grow your business here.</b></span></a></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Where is Keenlo available?\r\n</b></span><span class=\"s2\">Keenlo is available everywhere! During our beta program, we’re in select communities around the US and Europe. But we have many Gurus offering classes and services around the world.Our full backend software currently supports fitness businesses in the United States, Canada, the UK, and Ireland, and will be expanding to more countries soon!</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s2\">Any fitness business or professional, anywhere, can add their classes or services to Keenlo for free.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>I don’t see my favorite studio / class / fit pro on Keenlo. What do I do?\r\n</b></span><span class=\"s2\">Drop us a line and tell us who’s missing! Suggest your favorite studio or class <a href=\"mailto:team@keenlo.com\"><span class=\"s3\"><b>here</b></span></a>.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Can I use a class pass?\r\n</b></span><span class=\"s2\">Yes! If the studio you attend allows you to book classes through Keenlo, your class pass will be saved in your profile, and will apply to any classes you book at that studio through Keenlo.</span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>What’s with the “Keenloco”?\r\n</b></span><span class=\"s2\">We believe that fitness should be fun! The Guru is our daily reminder to sweat, laugh and enjoy life. She’s always there to encourage you to get sweaty, to try something new, and to not take life—or fitness—too seriously.</span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Who can use Keenlo?\r\n</b></span><span class=\"s2\">Keenlo is for everyone: yogis, gym goers, pilates fiends, spin addicts, fitness newbies, zumba lovers, and more.</span></li>\r\n</ul>',	'FAQ',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'faq',	'',	'',	'2014-07-14 05:04:50',	'2014-07-14 05:04:50',	'',	0,	'http://keenlo.com/?page_id=749',	0,	'page',	'',	0),
