(1235,	1,	'2014-08-20 14:28:45',	'2014-08-20 14:28:45',	'Rebecca is passionate about living a healthy lifestyle, this passion drives her to listen to her body, research, learn, share and coach. To Rebecca, healthy living is not only about the food we eat, its the choices we make, the actions we take and the thoughts in our minds.\r\n\r\nRebecca holds one on one sessions with clients to support them with their health goals in nourishing their body step by step to achieve a holistic healthier version of themselves over the course of a wellness programme.\r\n\r\nShe can teach you fast and easy new cooking techniques, give you recipes, write you menu plans, support you side by side in your health goals, train you in new ways to achieve balance in your life and de-stress. Ultimately showing you how accessible a healthy life is, even with a busy schedule!\r\n\r\nHow it works:\r\nRebecca will meet with you for a free 45min consultation in person or via Skype. You will have a one on one consultation about your needs and then move forward with the best possible plan to cater to health and happiness!\r\n\r\nWellness &amp; Food Coaching: $130/1hr session\r\n\r\nSessions available via Skype or in person 5-10 sessions recommended',	'Cooking Classes',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'closed',	'',	'cooking-classes',	'',	'',	'2014-08-20 14:29:27',	'2014-08-20 14:29:27',	'',	0,	'https://keenlo.com/service/cooking-classes/',	0,	'product',	'',	0),
(1236,	1,	'2014-08-20 14:30:52',	'2014-08-20 14:30:52',	'<strong>How it works:</strong>\nI will meet with you for a free 45min intro consultation in person or via Skype. From the get go I will meet you where you\'re at and together we will unveil your wellness desires. During this consultation we will set an intention together and then let your expansion, growth and creativity flow!\n\nBOOK YOUR FREE 30MIN INTRO CONSULTATION\nWellness &amp; Food Coaching: $130 : 60min session\n\nSessions available via Skype or in person at my Rozelle, Sydney office 10 sessions recommended to achieve lasting results',	'Wholistic Wellness Food Coaching',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'923-autosave-v1',	'',	'',	'2014-08-20 14:30:52',	'2014-08-20 14:30:52',	'',	923,	'https://keenlo.com/923-autosave-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(1237,	1,	'2014-08-20 14:36:29',	'2014-08-20 14:36:29',	'<strong>Private Conscious Cooking Demonstrations &amp; Classes:</strong>\nWanting something a little more intimate? Learn to cook in your own home! I love nothing more than to pay it forward and spread the love, what better place to do it than in your own kitchen. Let\'s together- cook, share, eat and express creativity.\n\nMy private cooking classes are designed completely around you! I offer an opportunity for a convenient and personalised approach to learning how to cook. Enhance your knowledge about Nutrition, Superfoods, Wholefoods &amp; Healing foods.\n\nIf you want to have a girls night in and hit the pans, learn to create a lovers dinner, discover dude food, create exciting food with dietary restraints or expand your cooking knowledge and learn professional techniques, a workshop is the best place to start.\n\nI specialise in healthy versions of old classics and creating new tantalizing dishes that will have you looking every bit the master chef at your next dinner party, you\'ll love it!\n\nMy varied classes use chemical free produce, organic meats/dairy and sustainable fish where possible. Be it vegetarian, gluten free, diary free, refined sugar free, super foods or your own ideas, we can get creative and expand your knowledge while having a blast!\n\nDon\'t even think twice, get in contact to discuss booking your private tutorial in your home today.\n\n&nbsp;\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: 400; color: rgba(68, 68, 68, 0.901961);\">Choose from...</h3>\n<h2 style=\"font-weight: 400; color: #49caaa;\"><em>Private Conscious Cooking Demonstrations in your home</em></h2>\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: 400; color: rgba(68, 68, 68, 0.901961);\">Demo Style $150pp vegetarian/$165pp meat &amp; seafood (min 4 people/max 10) 2.5 hrs with meal &amp; recipes, complimentary organic wine and canape included.</h3>\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: 400; color: rgba(68, 68, 68, 0.901961);\"><em>***For more than 10 students please contact me to discuss options***</em></h3>\n&nbsp;\n<h2 style=\"font-weight: 400; color: #49caaa;\"><em>Private Conscious Cooking Lessons in</em> <em>your home</em></h2>\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: 400; color: rgba(68, 68, 68, 0.901961);\">One on One/Hands On $80hr weekdays/$95hr weekends, excluding food costs (min 3 hrs).</h3>\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: 400; color: rgba(68, 68, 68, 0.901961);\">There are two options here, I can come and cook with you in your kitchen with your existing ingredients and teach you tips and techniques (I specialise in ready steady cook scenarios). Or you can select your own recipes or recipes from my archives and we can shop together and I can teach you where to shop and then prepare the meal together in your home.</h3>\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: 400; color: rgba(68, 68, 68, 0.901961);\"><em>***For each additional student please add $25 an hr, up to 4. For numbers over 4 please contact me to discuss options***</em></h3>',	'Cooking Classes',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'1235-autosave-v1',	'',	'',	'2014-08-20 14:36:29',	'2014-08-20 14:36:29',	'',	1235,	'https://keenlo.com/1235-autosave-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
