(78,	77,	'shop_vendor',	'\"Do something today that your future self will thank you for\" PT sessions available for all different levels of fitness. I\'m specialised in strength &amp; conditioning, boxing classes, specific sport conditioning and rehab.\r\n\r\n\"DATE &amp; FIT Bootcamps\" New rules, new concept bootcamp; \" DATE FIT bootcamps\" will offer you a new way to meet people through intensive workout challenges. Every weekend, different theme and different people to meet and share the same passion of fitness… so NO EXCUSE, jump on board…. Limited to 20 people per group session.\r\n\r\nABOUT YOUR PERSONAL TRAINER:\r\n\r\nEDOUARD or \"ED\" is a qualified Personal Trainer and Sports Trainer accredited by Fitness Australia. He was born in Australia but raised in France. After few years in tactical response unit in a \"French Police force\" he came back to Sydney strong with high intensity fitness experience. He passed his certificates III &amp; IV in Fitness and also Sports trainer and have been demanded for his enjoyable and tough trainings. He coaches either in French or English and have decided to focus his PT trainings for people that really want to commit and get fast results.\r\n\r\nHis bootcamps are innovating as he believes in get fit through fun experience!\r\n\" People in Sydney love sports and party, why can\'t we combined those two worlds together\" his words inspired him to create a new way to meet people with fun bootcamp. \"sharing and enduring the same pain together, break all the barriers…\"',	0,	4),
(80,	15,	'product_type',	'',	0,	17),
(81,	79,	'shop_vendor',	'All classes will raise your heart-rate, guaranteed to break a sweat. As well as yoga and pilates, we also run a free community bootcamp for mums to help them get back their fitness and energy after birth. We have a variety of locations, and a nanny available at most classes.\r\n\r\nA LITTLE ABOUT NICOLE:\r\n\r\nNicole finished her Bachelor of Science in Exercise Physiology in America then went on to work in the pharmaceutical industry for 10 years. After starting her own young family, her passion became dedicated to learning how better to stay healthy, and how better to PREVENT disease rather than treat it too late with medicines. She trained in yoga &amp; pilates and opened up a organic &amp; whole foods business. She is also well connected in the raw vegan &amp; organic community, volunteering her time at local organic coops and related organisations.',	0,	2),
(83,	81,	'shop_vendor',	'Sydney Pro Surf School it\'s a mobile surf school located in Sydney NSW. We just follow the best swell, to learn in safe conditions, and have a lot of fun. We provide a taste of the life that we lead as surfers, the freedom to ride waves, the ability to respect one another, and live in the positive.',	0,	1),
(85,	83,	'shop_vendor',	'Mestra Meirelou, born in Moji Guacu, Sao Paulo, began practicing Capoeira in 1992. She began to study under Mestre Peixe Ensaboado of Grupo Capoeira Brasil as one of Peixe’s first students in Australia.\r\nIn 1995 Mestra Meirelou moved back to Brazil with her husband and new born daughter for a year where she trained with Mestre Railson of Grupo Capoeira Gerais, Sul da Bahia. During this time she also had the opportunity to meet and participate in workshops with Mestres such as Ezequiel, Suassuna, Medicina, Mao Branca, Curumin, Bocao, Antonio Dias, Zumbi and many others.\r\n\r\nIn Rio de Janeiro, the birth place of Capoeira Brazil Group, Meirelou also practiced, periodically, with Mestres and Contra-Mestres such as M. Paulinho Sabia, Mestre Espiga and M.Curumin, M.Cabeca, M.Girino, M.Indio, M.Leo Pivete, M. TiTiTi, and M. Magali, M. Trapo, M. Fuinha, all from Group Capoeira Brasil, also from other groups such Senzala: M.Toni Vargas, M.Ramos, M.Peixinho, M.Sorriso, M.Itamar among others.',	0,	2),
