(133,	130,	'shop_vendor',	'At Core Dynamics we create tailored Pilates and general fitness programs for men and women of all ages and abilities.\r\n\r\nWe have a passion for teaching our clients and take the utmost care and time to deliver a quality class.\r\n\r\nRegular practice of Pilates can assist:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>shaping and toning of the body</li>\r\n	<li>weight loss</li>\r\n	<li>injury management and rehabilitation</li>\r\n	<li>increased fitness and strength</li>\r\n	<li>improved posture and core strength</li>\r\n	<li>improved flexibility and balance</li>\r\n</ul>',	0,	2),
(134,	131,	'product_cat',	'',	0,	3),
(135,	132,	'shop_vendor',	'<strong>YOGARAMA</strong>\r\nYogarama teaches the benefits of yoga to students of all ages from 8 to 80.\r\n\r\nFor adults, Yogarama has Hatha vinyasa yoga classes on the sunny deck at Wylie\'s Bath in Coogee with stunning ocean views. From July-October, yoga classes are in a warm wintery haven on the deck.\r\n\r\nFor kids, we offer Yogarama-Drama camps in the holidays and kids classes after school.\r\n\r\nDr Daniella Goldberg is the founder of Yogarama. She has been practising yoga since she was 5 years old and qualified as yoga teacher in 2013 in Sydney.',	0,	1),
