(150,	142,	'shop_vendor',	'The <strong>Aussie Footvolley</strong> was created by two Brazilians footvolley lovers!\r\nAfter a few years of experience with the sport we have found ourselves passionate about it and really ready to bring it into the most beautiful beaches in the world. The essential focus of Aussie Footvolley is to support and promote the growth of footvolley in the whole continent. The Aussie Footvolley will offer training and educational opportunities designed for both the physical and mental skills necessary to master the sport.',	0,	1),
